DESCRIPTION

Mail-Convert-Mbox-ToEml is a Module to convert MBox mail files from Mozilla and
Co to Outlook Express single .eml which can be imported to Outlook and Outlook
Express.  I could only test MBox files from Mozilla on WindowsXP and Windows
2000.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  none

